otus_raw <- read.csv(here("private_data","Dunthorn2017.txt"), stringsAsFactors = FALSE, sep = "\t")
#otu_tab <- otus_raw %>% as.data.frame() %>% column_to_rownames("X__1") %>% as.matrix()
otu_tab <- otus_raw %>% select(B005_B006:T199_T200) %>% as.matrix() %>% t()
otu_tab <- otu_tab[rowSums(otu_tab) > 2000 & rownames(otu_tab) != "B005_B006",]

mapping <- tibble(Sample = rownames(otu_tab)) %>% mutate(Origin = if_else(grepl("^B", Sample), "Panama", if_else(grepl("^L", Sample), "Costa Rica", "Ecuador")))
plot_mds_dunthorn <- function(base_mds, mapping, aligned_samples = NULL, show_paths = 0.5,  ...) {
  plot_mds(base_mds, mapping, aligned_samples = aligned_samples, color_aes = Origin, shape_aes = Origin, show_paths = show_paths, sample_point_alpha = 0.2) #+ scale_y_continuous(trans = "reverse") + scale_x_continuous(trans = "reverse")
}

set.seed(20190620)
for(i in 1:5) {
  samples_to_use <- mapping %>% group_by(Origin) %>% sample_n(3) %>% pull(Sample)
  otu_tab_filtered <- otu_tab[samples_to_use,]
  
  base_mds_filtered <- otu_tab_filtered %>% metaMDS(trymax = 400, maxit = 500, parallel = 1, trace = 0)
  mds_samples_dm_filtered <- sample_posterior_dm_all(20, otu_tab_filtered, prior = "ml",N_draws = "original") %>% 
    metaMDS_per_sample(trymax = 400, maxit = 500) %>% purrr::map(vegan::procrustes, X = base_mds_filtered)
  
  pl <- plot_mds_dunthorn(base_mds_filtered, mapping, aligned_samples = mds_samples_dm_filtered, show_paths = "all") 
  print(pl)
  print(pl + facet_wrap(~Origin))
  
  groups <- data.frame(observation = rownames(base_mds_filtered$points)) %>% inner_join(mapping, by = c("observation" = "Sample")) %>% pull("Origin")
  print(connectivity_all_groups(base_mds_filtered$points, mds_samples_dm_filtered %>% purrr::map(~ .x$Yrot), groups))

}
